  <name>Color My Desktop</name>
  <summary>Personalize your desktop with custom generated themes using colors you choose</summary>

  <description>
    <p>
      Color My Desktop is designed to give you full control over 
      your Gnome-shell, KDE Plasma, GTK4 apps, Nautilus, Zen-Browser, and even Vesktop aesthetics.
    </p>
    <ul>
  <li>Creates and manages custom color palettes.</li>
  <li>Generates and applies matching themes using selected color pallete.</li>
  <li>Supports uniform themes for numerous apps and system UI elements.</li>
  </ul>
  </description>


